          %p.detail-info.speaker__talk Escaping Reality With Shoes
          %p.detail-info Let's imagine for a moment, you have the day off and all of your friends are out of town&hellip; and it's raining!
          %p.detail-info What are you going to do with all of that free time?
          %p.detail-info There are so many options, and one of my personal favorites is hacking on some random idea or experiementing with code.
          %p.detail-info It's important to step out of your comfort zone, and in this talk we will go one step further into the Magical Land of Shoes.
          %p.detail-info Let's catch up on the last few years of the project, the future, and all of the amazing things you can build with it. Yours truly will give you a whirlwind tour of what Shoes is capable of and together build an experience that we can share for a lifetime.
      %li.detail-section#segal
        %img.speaker__pic.speaker__pic--detail{src: '/speakers/loren.jpg', alt: 'Loren Segal'}
        .speaker-info
          %h2.detail-title Loren Segal
          .speaker__links
